    <title>Polymorphism</title>
    <para>
        JPQL statements are polymorphic: all statement elements
        which apply to a target bean also apply to all its specializations.
    </para>
    <para>
        This allows one to use <emphasis>abstraction</emphasis> to develop
        very general and flexible domain models that would be difficult
        to implement manually using relational data structures.
    </para>
